casebody.head_matter:
In the Matter of DISCIPLINE OF LeslieAnn HAACKE.
No. D-2745.
Supreme Court of the United States
Nov. 12, 2013.
LeslieAnn Haacke, of Scottsdale, Arizona, is suspended from the practice of law in this Court and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring her to show cause why she should not disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
